{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I'm here today to share with you"},{"time":3000,"text":"an extraordinary journey -"},{"time":5000,"text":"extraordinarily rewarding journey,\nactually -"},{"time":8000,"text":"which brought me into"},{"time":10000,"text":"training rats"},{"time":12000,"text":"to save human lives"},{"time":14000,"text":"by detecting landmines"},{"time":16000,"text":"and tuberculosis."},{"time":18000,"text":"As a child, I had two passions."},{"time":21000,"text":"One was a passion for rodents."},{"time":24000,"text":"I had all kinds of rats,"},{"time":26000,"text":"mice, hamsters,"},{"time":28000,"text":"gerbils, squirrels."},{"time":30000,"text":"You name it, I bred it, and I sold them to pet shops."},{"time":33000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":35000,"text":"I also had a passion for Africa."},{"time":38000,"text":"Growing up in a multicultural environment,"},{"time":40000,"text":"we had African students in the house,"},{"time":42000,"text":"and I learned about their stories,"},{"time":44000,"text":"so different backgrounds,"},{"time":46000,"text":"dependency on imported know-how,"},{"time":49000,"text":"goods, services,"},{"time":51000,"text":"exuberant cultural diversity."},{"time":54000,"text":"Africa was truly fascinating for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56000,"text":"I became an industrial engineer,"},{"time":58000,"text":"engineer in product development,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and I focused on appropriate detection technologies,"},{"time":63000,"text":"actually the first appropriate technologies"},{"time":65000,"text":"for developing countries."},{"time":68000,"text":"I started working in the industry,"},{"time":70000,"text":"but I wasn't really happy to contribute"},{"time":72000,"text":"to a material consumer society"},{"time":75000,"text":"in a linear, extracting"},{"time":78000,"text":"and manufacturing mode."},{"time":80000,"text":"I quit my job to focus on the real world problem:"},{"time":82000,"text":"landmines."},{"time":85000,"text":"We're talking '95 now."},{"time":88000,"text":"Princess Diana is announcing on TV"},{"time":91000,"text":"that landmines form a structural barrier"},{"time":93000,"text":"to any development, which is really true."},{"time":96000,"text":"As long as these devices are there,"},{"time":98000,"text":"or there is suspicion of landmines,"},{"time":100000,"text":"you can't really enter into the land."},{"time":102000,"text":"Actually, there was an appeal worldwide"},{"time":104000,"text":"for new detectors"},{"time":107000,"text":"sustainable in the environments"},{"time":109000,"text":"where they're needed to produce,"},{"time":111000,"text":"which is mainly in the developing world."},{"time":113000,"text":"We chose rats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"Why would you choose rats?"},{"time":117000,"text":"Because, aren't they vermin?"},{"time":119000,"text":"Well, actually rats are,"},{"time":121000,"text":"in contrary to what most people think about them,"},{"time":123000,"text":"rats are highly sociable creatures."},{"time":127000,"text":"And actually, our product -- what you see here."},{"time":130000,"text":"There's a target somewhere here."},{"time":132000,"text":"You see an operator, a trained African"},{"time":134000,"text":"with his rats in front"},{"time":136000,"text":"who actually are left and right."},{"time":138000,"text":"There, the animal finds a mine."},{"time":140000,"text":"It scratches on the soil."},{"time":142000,"text":"And the animal comes back for a food reward."},{"time":145000,"text":"Very, very simple."},{"time":147000,"text":"Very sustainable in this environment."},{"time":150000,"text":"Here, the animal gets its food reward."},{"time":153000,"text":"And that's how it works."},{"time":155000,"text":"Very, very simple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"Now why would you use rats?"},{"time":159000,"text":"Rats have been used since the '50s last century,"},{"time":161000,"text":"in all kinds of experiments."},{"time":164000,"text":"Rats have more genetic material"},{"time":167000,"text":"allocated to olfaction"},{"time":169000,"text":"than any other mammal species."},{"time":171000,"text":"They're extremely sensitive to smell."},{"time":174000,"text":"Moreover, they have the mechanisms to map all these smells"},{"time":177000,"text":"and to communicate about it."},{"time":180000,"text":"Now how do we communicate with rats?"},{"time":182000,"text":"Well don't talk rat,"},{"time":185000,"text":"but we have a clicker,"},{"time":187000,"text":"a standard method for animal training,"},{"time":189000,"text":"which you see there."},{"time":191000,"text":"A clicker, which makes a particular sound"},{"time":194000,"text":"with which you can reinforce particular behaviors."},{"time":197000,"text":"First of all, we associate the click sound with a food reward,"},{"time":200000,"text":"which is smashed banana and peanuts together in a syringe."},{"time":204000,"text":"Once the animal knows click, food,"},{"time":206000,"text":"click, food, click, food --"},{"time":208000,"text":"so click is food --"},{"time":210000,"text":"we bring it in a cage with a hole,"},{"time":212000,"text":"and actually the animal learns"},{"time":214000,"text":"to stick the nose in the hole"},{"time":216000,"text":"under which a target scent is placed,"},{"time":218000,"text":"and to do that for five seconds --"},{"time":220000,"text":"five seconds, which is long for a rat."},{"time":222000,"text":"Once the animal knows this, we make the task a bit more difficult."},{"time":225000,"text":"It learns how to find the target smell"},{"time":228000,"text":"in a cage with several holes, up to 10 holes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"Then the animal learns"},{"time":233000,"text":"to walk on a leash in the open"},{"time":235000,"text":"and find targets."},{"time":237000,"text":"In the next step, animals learn"},{"time":240000,"text":"to find real mines in real minefields."},{"time":242000,"text":"They are tested and accredited"},{"time":245000,"text":"according to International Mine Action Standards,"},{"time":247000,"text":"just like dogs have to pass a test."},{"time":250000,"text":"This consists of 400 square meters."},{"time":252000,"text":"There's a number of mines"},{"time":255000,"text":"placed blindly,"},{"time":257000,"text":"and the team of trainer and their rat"},{"time":260000,"text":"have to find all the targets."},{"time":264000,"text":"If the animal does that, it gets a license"},{"time":267000,"text":"as an accredited animal"},{"time":269000,"text":"to be operational in the field --"},{"time":271000,"text":"just like dogs, by the way."},{"time":273000,"text":"Maybe one slight difference:"},{"time":275000,"text":"we can train rats at a fifth of the price"},{"time":278000,"text":"of training the mining dog."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280000,"text":"This is our team in Mozambique:"},{"time":282000,"text":"one Tanzanian trainer,"},{"time":284000,"text":"who transfers the skills"},{"time":286000,"text":"to these three Mozambican fellows."},{"time":288000,"text":"And you should see the pride in the eyes of these people."},{"time":291000,"text":"They have a skill,"},{"time":293000,"text":"which makes them much less dependent"},{"time":295000,"text":"on foreign aid."},{"time":297000,"text":"Moreover, this small team"},{"time":300000,"text":"together with, of course, you need the heavy vehicles"},{"time":303000,"text":"and the manual de-miners to follow-up."},{"time":306000,"text":"But with this small investment in a rat capacity,"},{"time":309000,"text":"we have demonstrated in Mozambique"},{"time":312000,"text":"that we can reduce the cost-price per square meter"},{"time":315000,"text":"up to 60 percent"},{"time":317000,"text":"of what is currently normal --"},{"time":319000,"text":"two dollars per square meter, we do it at $1.18,"},{"time":321000,"text":"and we can still bring that price down."},{"time":323000,"text":"Question of scale."},{"time":325000,"text":"If you can bring in more rats,"},{"time":327000,"text":"we can actually make the output even bigger."},{"time":329000,"text":"We have a demonstration site in Mozambique."},{"time":332000,"text":"Eleven African governments"},{"time":335000,"text":"have seen that they can become less dependent"},{"time":338000,"text":"by using this technology."},{"time":340000,"text":"They have signed the pact for peace"},{"time":342000,"text":"and treaty in the Great Lakes region,"},{"time":345000,"text":"and they endorse hero rats"},{"time":348000,"text":"to clear their common borders of landmines."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"But let me bring you to a very different problem."},{"time":354000,"text":"And there's about 6,000 people last year"},{"time":356000,"text":"that walked on a landmine,"},{"time":358000,"text":"but worldwide last year,"},{"time":360000,"text":"almost 1.9 million died from tuberculosis"},{"time":362000,"text":"as a first cause of infection."},{"time":366000,"text":"Especially in Africa"},{"time":368000,"text":"where T.B. and HIV are strongly linked,"},{"time":371000,"text":"there is a huge common problem."},{"time":376000,"text":"Microscopy, the standard WHO procedure,"},{"time":379000,"text":"reaches from 40 to 60 percent reliability."},{"time":383000,"text":"In Tanzania -- the numbers don't lie --"},{"time":386000,"text":"45 percent of people -- T.B. patients --"},{"time":389000,"text":"get diagnosed with T.B. before they die."},{"time":393000,"text":"It means that, if you have T.B.,"},{"time":396000,"text":"you have more chance that you won't be detected,"},{"time":398000,"text":"but will just die from T.B. secondary infections and so on."},{"time":405000,"text":"And if, however,"},{"time":407000,"text":"you are detected very early, diagnosed early,"},{"time":409000,"text":"treatment can start,"},{"time":411000,"text":"and even in HIV-positives, it makes sense."},{"time":414000,"text":"You can actually cure T.B.,"},{"time":416000,"text":"even in HIV-positives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419000,"text":"So in our common language, Dutch,"},{"time":422000,"text":"the name for T.B."},{"time":424000,"text":"is \"tering,\""},{"time":426000,"text":"which, etymologically,"},{"time":428000,"text":"refers to the smell of tar."},{"time":431000,"text":"Already the old Chinese"},{"time":433000,"text":"and the Greek, Hippocrates,"},{"time":436000,"text":"have actually published,"},{"time":438000,"text":"documented, that T.B. can be diagnosed"},{"time":441000,"text":"based on the volatiles"},{"time":443000,"text":"exuding from patients."},{"time":446000,"text":"So what we did is we collected some samples --"},{"time":448000,"text":"just as a way of testing --"},{"time":450000,"text":"from hospitals,"},{"time":452000,"text":"trained rats on them"},{"time":455000,"text":"and see if this works,"},{"time":457000,"text":"and wonder, well,"},{"time":459000,"text":"we can reach 89 percent sensitivity,"},{"time":461000,"text":"86 percent specificity"},{"time":463000,"text":"using multiple rats in a row."},{"time":465000,"text":"This is how it works,"},{"time":468000,"text":"and really, this is a generic technology."},{"time":471000,"text":"We're talking now explosives, tuberculosis,"},{"time":474000,"text":"but can you imagine,"},{"time":476000,"text":"you can actually put anything under there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478000,"text":"So how does it work?"},{"time":480000,"text":"You have a cassette with 10 samples."},{"time":482000,"text":"You put these 10 samples at once in the cage."},{"time":485000,"text":"An animal only needs two hundredths of a second"},{"time":487000,"text":"to discriminate the scent, so it goes extremely fast."},{"time":490000,"text":"Here it's already at the third sample."},{"time":493000,"text":"This is a positive sample."},{"time":497000,"text":"It gets a click sound and comes for the food reward."},{"time":502000,"text":"And by doing so, very fast,"},{"time":504000,"text":"we can have like a second-line opinion"},{"time":507000,"text":"to see which patients are positive,"},{"time":509000,"text":"which are negative."},{"time":512000,"text":"Just as an indication,"},{"time":514000,"text":"whereas a microscopist can process"},{"time":516000,"text":"40 samples in a day,"},{"time":518000,"text":"a rat can process"},{"time":520000,"text":"the same amount of samples"},{"time":522000,"text":"in seven minutes only."},{"time":524000,"text":"A cage like this --"},{"time":526000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":531000,"text":"A cage like this -- provided that you have rats,"},{"time":534000,"text":"and we have now currently"},{"time":536000,"text":"25 tuberculosis rats --"},{"time":538000,"text":"a cage like this, operating throughout the day,"},{"time":541000,"text":"can process 1,680 samples."},{"time":546000,"text":"Can you imagine the potential offspring applications --"},{"time":549000,"text":"environmental detection"},{"time":551000,"text":"of pollutants in soils,"},{"time":553000,"text":"customs applications,"},{"time":555000,"text":"detection of illicit goods in containers and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559000,"text":"But let's stick first to tuberculosis."},{"time":561000,"text":"I just want to briefly highlight,"},{"time":563000,"text":"the blue rods"},{"time":565000,"text":"are the scores of microscopy only"},{"time":567000,"text":"at the five clinics in Dar es Salaam"},{"time":570000,"text":"on a population of 500,000 people,"},{"time":572000,"text":"where 15,000 reported to get a test done."},{"time":575000,"text":"Microscopy for 1,800 patients."},{"time":578000,"text":"And by just presenting the samples once more to the rats"},{"time":582000,"text":"and looping those results back,"},{"time":585000,"text":"we were able to increase case detection rates"},{"time":587000,"text":"by over 30 percent."},{"time":589000,"text":"Throughout last year,"},{"time":591000,"text":"we've been -- depending on which intervals you take --"},{"time":593000,"text":"we've been consistently"},{"time":595000,"text":"increasing case detection rates"},{"time":597000,"text":"in five hospitals in Dar es Salaam"},{"time":599000,"text":"between 30 and 40 percent."},{"time":602000,"text":"So this is really considerable."},{"time":604000,"text":"Knowing that a missed patient by microscopy"},{"time":606000,"text":"infects up to 15 people,"},{"time":608000,"text":"healthy people, per year,"},{"time":610000,"text":"you can be sure"},{"time":612000,"text":"that we have saved lots of lives."},{"time":614000,"text":"At least our hero rats have saved lots of lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617000,"text":"The way forward for us"},{"time":619000,"text":"is now to standardize this technology."},{"time":621000,"text":"And there are simple things"},{"time":623000,"text":"like, for instance, we have a small laser in the sniffer hole"},{"time":627000,"text":"where the animal has to stick for five seconds."},{"time":629000,"text":"So, to standardize this."},{"time":631000,"text":"Also, to standardize the pellets,"},{"time":633000,"text":"the food rewards,"},{"time":635000,"text":"and to semi-automate this"},{"time":637000,"text":"in order to replicate this on a much larger scale"},{"time":640000,"text":"and affect the lives of many more people."},{"time":643000,"text":"To conclude, there are also other applications at the horizon."},{"time":646000,"text":"Here is a first prototype"},{"time":648000,"text":"of our camera rat,"},{"time":650000,"text":"which is a rat with a rat backpack"},{"time":652000,"text":"with a camera that can go under rubble"},{"time":654000,"text":"to detect for victims"},{"time":656000,"text":"after earthquake and so on."},{"time":658000,"text":"This is in a prototype stage."},{"time":660000,"text":"We don't have a working system here yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663000,"text":"To conclude, I would actually like to say,"},{"time":666000,"text":"you may think this is about rats, these projects,"},{"time":668000,"text":"but in the end it is about people."},{"time":670000,"text":"It is about empowering vulnerable communities"},{"time":672000,"text":"to tackle difficult, expensive"},{"time":675000,"text":"and dangerous humanitarian detection tasks,"},{"time":678000,"text":"and doing that with a local resource,"},{"time":681000,"text":"plenty available."},{"time":683000,"text":"So something completely different"},{"time":686000,"text":"is to keep on challenging your perception"},{"time":689000,"text":"about the resources surrounding you,"},{"time":692000,"text":"whether they are environmental,"},{"time":695000,"text":"technological, animal, or human."},{"time":700000,"text":"And to respectfully harmonize with them"},{"time":703000,"text":"in order to foster a sustainable world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":708000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}